Police are looking for JP Kagunduini ward MCA nominee Peter Muthoni after a Nairobi court issued a warrant of arrest on Tuesday for skipping his hearing. He is facing fraud charges. Muthoni is accused of defrauding Alice Wanjiku (pictured) of Sh2.2 million between June 18 and 29 last year at Pioneer House, Nairobi. He allegedly pretended he a could sell her a car and presented himself as Solomon Kamau Nyingi.